name: MEC Knox Cardholder
description: Stay on top of your cards and assorted currency while keeping everything secure and protected from ID theft.Made of polyester with a water resistant coating.Aluminum RFID shield layer sandwiched between lining and outer fabric prevents information theft from your chipped cards.Clamshell access to interior uses a luggage grade YKK zipper.Internal divider holds paper currency with room for 5 to 6 cards.
